82
00:05:04,095 --> 00:05:05,555
-When is it?
-This Saturday.

83
00:05:05,639 --> 00:05:07,140
-Saturday?
-Okay…

84
00:05:07,682 --> 00:05:10,101
-Seriously?
-Can you please put that down?

85
00:05:10,185 --> 00:05:11,728
You always wield it as a weapon.

86
00:05:11,812 --> 00:05:13,396
Mom, this Saturday--

87
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:16,191
You, get the money back tomorrow.

88
00:05:16,274 --> 00:05:18,235
If you don't, you're dead meat!

89
00:05:18,318 --> 00:05:22,948
The thing is, Ji-sun left for Macau
on a business trip today--

90
00:05:23,031 --> 00:05:25,075
