91
00:05:25,158 --> 00:05:27,911
Hey, Shin Gi-heon! You…

92
00:05:32,541 --> 00:05:33,792
What the hell?

93
00:05:33,875 --> 00:05:36,628
Did you just throw <i>jokbal</i>
into my handsome face?

94
00:05:36,711 --> 00:05:38,922
I don't want to talk to you, so leave.

95
00:05:39,005 --> 00:05:40,298
Get out right now!

96
00:05:40,382 --> 00:05:42,968
Why must I be ashamed
of lending someone my money?

97
00:05:43,051 --> 00:05:45,554
How is that yours?
I gave you that pocket money.

98
00:05:45,637 --> 00:05:47,222
I can no longer

99
00:05:48,848 --> 00:05:50,350
live like this anymore!

100
00:05:52,477 --> 00:05:53,645
Dad?

101
00:05:56,731 --> 00:05:59,025
Fine, I can't stand it, either!

102
00:06:01,444 --> 00:06:02,487
Mom?

103
00:06:07,534 --> 00:06:10,078
I'm sorry, but I'm not in the mood
to hear you singing.

104
00:06:10,161 --> 00:06:13,164
I need all of you here to stay motivated,
so sit tight.

105
00:06:21,506 --> 00:06:22,340
Hello?

106
00:06:22,424 --> 00:06:26,303
Yes, this is number 178, Jeong Jin-hwan!

107
00:06:27,679 --> 00:06:29,723
Should I start singing? Yes, sir!

108
00:06:41,443 --> 00:06:44,154
<i>Excuse me. Start from the refrain.</i>

109
00:06:44,237 --> 00:06:46,531
The refrain? Got it, sir.

110
00:06:46,615 --> 00:06:48,533
I'll start over then.

111
00:06:50,285 --> 00:06:53,705
<i>It's love, it's love</i>

112
00:06:53,788 --> 00:06:57,292
<i>Even if I erase it, it's still love</i>

113
00:06:57,375 --> 00:07:01,129
<i>I try to let go of you</i>

114
00:07:01,212 --> 00:07:04,591
<i>But you're the only one living in my heart</i>

115
00:07:04,674 --> 00:07:08,303
<i>Only you, only you</i>

116
00:07:08,386 --> 00:07:12,057
<i>You're the one I yearn and long for</i>

117
00:07:12,140 --> 00:07:15,894
<i>I take out a photo of you</i>

118
00:07:16,478 --> 00:07:20,899
<i>And gaze at it as I fall asleep</i>

119
00:07:21,608 --> 00:07:23,485
<i>You made the first cut.</i>

120
00:07:28,531 --> 00:07:31,493
Thank you. Thank you so much.
Have a good day.

121
00:07:34,704 --> 00:07:36,164
Yes. I made it!

122
00:07:36,915 --> 00:07:40,085
Guys! I'll be making my debut.

123
00:07:40,168 --> 00:07:43,171
Do you have to go to Osan
for the second round, though?

124
00:07:43,254 --> 00:07:44,214
Of course.

125
00:07:44,297 --> 00:07:47,926
Ha-young, I'll promise
to say your name out loud on TV.

126
00:07:48,009 --> 00:07:50,053
You'll all come with me, right?

127
00:07:50,637 --> 00:07:53,932
Well, I can't say for sure.

128
00:07:54,808 --> 00:07:56,810
If my Brother can't say for sure,

129
00:07:57,727 --> 00:07:58,812
then neither can I.

130
00:07:58,895 --> 00:08:02,273
Come on, Sol-i.
You have to come over. What's wrong?

131
00:08:05,568 --> 00:08:07,529
