132
00:08:18,498 --> 00:08:20,125
<i>I'm going to another city.</i>

133
00:08:20,750 --> 00:08:22,544
<i>Don't wait up for me, and go to bed.</i>

134
00:08:44,149 --> 00:08:44,983
