OSAN, 2ND PRELIMINARY ROUND

183
00:12:27,288 --> 00:12:28,331
BECOME AN IDOL
HANDSOME JIN-HWAN

184
00:12:31,834 --> 00:12:35,797
<i>Making you my lady</i>

185
00:12:35,880 --> 00:12:38,383
<i>became a dream of mine</i>

186
00:12:38,925 --> 00:12:44,639
<i>I will make it happen
No matter the obstacles</i>

187
00:12:50,853 --> 00:12:52,271
<i>My dream used to be</i>

188
00:12:52,355 --> 00:12:53,940
<i>Becoming the President, my dad's favorite</i>

189
00:12:54,023 --> 00:12:56,693
<i>A friend of mine shared that dream…</i>

190
00:12:56,776 --> 00:12:59,112
Thank you for coming. Next.

191
00:12:59,612 --> 00:13:02,448
I have another song prepared.
Please give me another chance.

192
00:13:04,075 --> 00:13:06,828
<i>Please love me</i>

193
00:13:06,911 --> 00:13:09,455
<i>Don't bring tears to my eyes</i>

194
00:13:15,378 --> 00:13:16,254
Damn it.

195
00:13:17,046 --> 00:13:18,715
The judges have no eye for talent.

196
00:13:19,215 --> 00:13:20,925
How can they disqualify a genius like me?

197
00:13:21,592 --> 00:13:24,095
Cheer up. You can try again
when they come to Suwon.

198
00:13:24,178 --> 00:13:27,098
He's right.
Just think of it as our little picnic.

199
00:13:27,181 --> 00:13:29,851
Since we're here,
why don't we spend the night here?

200
00:13:30,435 --> 00:13:33,271
Hey, is it because you want
to spend some time with Heon?

201
00:13:33,896 --> 00:13:36,357
Come on. It will be fun.

202
00:13:36,441 --> 00:13:39,652
Sounds good.
Let's have some fun while we're here.

203
00:13:40,570 --> 00:13:42,739
I can't. My mom will be worried.

204
00:13:42,822 --> 00:13:45,908
Comeo n, Ha-young.
We rarely get a chance like this.

205
00:13:45,992 --> 00:13:47,577
Then, let's vote on it.

206
00:13:48,828 --> 00:13:50,496
-I'm in.
-Me too.

207
00:13:50,580 --> 00:13:51,789
Me three.

208
00:14:00,298 --> 00:14:02,884
Let's find a place to sleep first.

209
00:14:04,469 --> 00:14:07,096
Shall we go over there?

210
00:14:09,640 --> 00:14:10,808
-Thank you!
-Thank you!

211
00:14:10,892 --> 00:14:12,810
-Have a good night.
-You, too.

212
00:14:14,312 --> 00:14:17,231
Hold on. Shouldn't we call home first?

213
00:14:17,815 --> 00:14:19,776
Right, let's do that.

214
00:14:23,237 --> 00:14:24,322
-Mom.
-Hey, Mom.

215
00:14:24,405 --> 00:14:25,948
I'm spending the night at Sol-i's.

216
00:14:26,032 --> 00:14:29,035
Ha-young offered to tutor me today
at her place.

217
00:14:29,118 --> 00:14:30,787
-Put her on?
-Put her on?

218
00:14:32,538 --> 00:14:33,790
-Hi.
-Hi, Mother.

219
00:14:33,873 --> 00:14:35,249
We won't stay up too late.

220
00:14:35,333 --> 00:14:36,876
We'll study for a few more hours.

221
00:14:36,959 --> 00:14:38,294
Don't worry.

222
00:14:38,378 --> 00:14:40,129
Sure, good night.

223
00:14:41,547 --> 00:14:44,342
-Hey, Mom.
-Mom, it's me. Good night.

224
00:14:46,803 --> 00:14:47,678
Nice!

225
00:14:48,262 --> 00:14:49,097
Hello?

226
00:14:49,680 --> 00:14:51,391
Mom, I'll sleep over
at my friend's place today!

227
00:14:54,310 --> 00:14:55,436
Please.

228
00:14:55,520 --> 00:14:56,854
Just this once.

229
00:15:04,695 --> 00:15:07,824
Hello, ma'am.
I'm Jin-hwan's classmate, Cha Heon.

230
00:15:09,492 --> 00:15:10,618
Right.

231
00:15:12,537 --> 00:15:14,580
Yes, thank you. Sure.

232
00:15:15,665 --> 00:15:17,083
Are we good?

233
00:15:26,717 --> 00:15:28,261
HEAD COACH

234
00:15:30,596 --> 00:15:32,432
-Hello?
-<i>Woo Dae-sung!</i>

235
00:15:33,099 --> 00:15:35,518
<i>Why did you skip training today,
and where are you?</i>

236
00:15:37,520 --> 00:15:39,730
I'm at a friend's house.

237
00:15:40,314 --> 00:15:43,526
<i>What? Then put that friend's father
on the phone!</i>

238
00:15:44,986 --> 00:15:46,112
Take it.

239
00:15:55,580 --> 00:15:56,414
Yes,

240
00:15:56,497 --> 00:15:59,333
I'm Jin-hwan's father.

241
00:15:59,417 --> 00:16:01,002
<i>Who are you trying to fool?</i>

242
00:16:01,085 --> 00:16:02,628
<i>Put your father on!</i>

243
00:16:05,006 --> 00:16:06,299
What the…

244
00:16:08,050 --> 00:16:08,926
Sorry.

245
00:16:09,010 --> 00:16:11,304
Don't answer your phone tonight.
That's better.

246
00:16:14,807 --> 00:16:17,393
Then I'll be dead once I get back.

247
00:16:20,062 --> 00:16:20,897
Thanks.

248
00:16:22,482 --> 00:16:24,901
Wow, that's a lot of stars.

249
00:16:25,526 --> 00:16:27,445
I know. They're really pretty.

250
00:16:28,279 --> 00:16:30,781
I've kept my nose
in my textbooks for so long,

251
00:16:30,865 --> 00:16:32,950
I didn't know how pretty the sky is.

252
00:16:33,993 --> 00:16:34,952
Hey, Jin-hwan.

253
00:16:35,661 --> 00:16:39,415
When did you bury your nose in your books?
You always dozed off in class.

254
00:16:39,499 --> 00:16:42,752
Can't you shut it
when I'm trying to be sentimental?

255
00:16:42,835 --> 00:16:44,670
Be quiet, both of you.

256
00:16:45,338 --> 00:16:47,882
Those stars may all look the same,

257
